snippet.title: Feudal Alloy - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Feudal Alloy is an epic action adventure with fish-controlled medieval robots!
Available on Steam, GOG, Nintendo Switch, PS4 and Xbox One.
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/699670
